so offers passenger car heavy duty diesel motorcycle and railroad and marine diesel engine oil additives as well as olefin copolymer viscosity index improvers afton chemical was founded in 00 and is headquartered in richmond va political donations   american chemistry council pac  0 american chemistry council pac  0 american chemistry council pac  0 american chemistry council pac  0 american chemistry council pac public holdings restricted data only for relsci professional users start my free trial ➤ see more other affiliations robert a shama is affiliated with newmarket corporation afton chemical corp youve reached your 0 free profiles limit this month upgrade to relsci pro today to enjoy unlimited article views and much more start my free trial ➤ still not convinced check out our full listing of features here are you a relsci pro subscriber login to relsci pro  ➤ not a pro subscriber log in here to manage your alerts keep me signed in login  ➤ forgot your password i have read the lexisnexis terms  conditions sign me up  ➤ news  events  afton chemical this website uses cookies to help us remember information about your viewing preferences and to improve features of the website we are legally required to obtain your consent before placing cookies on your computer please indicate whether you accept the use of cookies accept decline to configure and revoke your consent to the use of cookies please visit our cookie policy menu driveline additives learn more about driveline additives driveline additives insights and resources automotive gear automatic transmission fluid continuously variable transmission cvt dual clutch transmission dct manual transmission offroad power steering engine oil additives learn more about engine oil additives engine oil additives insights and resources olefin copolymer ocp vii heavy duty passenger car motorcycle fuel additives learn more about fuel additives fuel additives insights and resources light duty vehicle performance heavy duty vehic