aintain the integrity of certain elastomeric materials tackiness additives increase the adhesive properties of a lubricant thickeners  viscosity index improvers reduce the degree of change in lubricant viscosity contact news  events filter by all news  events news events sep 7 jul 7 jun 7 may 7 apr 7 mar 7 feb 7 jan 7 dec  nov  oct  sep  jul  jun  may  apr  mar  feb  jan  aug  view all sort by newest oldest afton chemical first additive company to receive top tier tm diesel approval richmond va july  – afton chemical announced today that its north american diesel performance additive dpa product line is the first in the industry to receive top tier™ diesel approval read more international congress drivetrain for vehicles july   germany read more afton chemical completes acquisition of aditivos mexicanos sa de cv richmond va july   – afton chemical corporation is pleased to announce the completion of its previously announced acquisition of aditivos mexicanos sa de cv amsa a petroleum additives manufacturing sales and distribution company based in mexico city mexico read more suggested content automotive in the fight against lspi afton is on the front lines industrial afton delivers unique lowfoam testing capabilities responsibility responsible care® robert a shama  executive bio compensation history and contacts  equilar atlas   log in  sign up x   as featured in robert a shama president afton chemical at newmarket corporation view full profile are you robert a shama claim your profile   sign up for equilar atlas and view robert a shamas full profile with equilar atlas you can identify corporate executives in robert a shamas network and community follow changes in robert a shamas employment and moneyinmotion connect with robert a shama through your network of contacts robert a shamas executive work history current president afton chemical newmarket corporation past to view robert a shamas complete executive work history sign up now age      robert a shamas biography 